msgstr ""

#: ../../content/repas/suivi-nutritionnel.md:201
msgid ""
"A **daily cron** refreshes the screening and creates **activities** for "
"residents who fall behind. Activities are capped at **once every 30 "
"days** per resident to avoid duplicates."
msgstr ""

